<h1 id="representing-information-digitally">Representing Information Digitally</h1>
<h2 id="bits-and-the-why-of-bytes">Bits and the ‚ÄúWhy‚Äù of bytes</h2>
<h2 id="learning-objectives">Learning objectives</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Explain the link between patterns, symbols, and information</li>
  <li>Determine possible PandA encodings using a physical phenomenon</li>
  <li>Enode and decode ASCII</li>
  <li>Represent numbers in binary form</li>
  <li>Compare different encoding methods</li>
  <li>Explain how structure tags (metadata) enode the Oxford English Dictionary</li>
